:: AD5A {"position":"6325,550","size":"100,100"}
Alexandra Bodovora: Thank you. Not many people understand. I will live for him; keep fighting for what he believed in, that way he will be with us always.

> (link-goto: "As long as our nation is alive, then those whose sacrifice have forged it will live on. *Slava Ukraini*", "AlexandraD5Understand")


:: AD5B {"position":"6450,550","size":"100,100"}
Alexandra Bodovora: He died a noble death, he’s a hero... Of course I am sad, but also proud. My son is an innocent, I will fight for him until my last breath.

> (link-goto: "I cannot understand your pain, but I implore you to rethink your decision to stay here... please Alexandra, you don’t deserve to die too. They're still evacuating civilians... There may not be another chance.", "AlexandraD5ProposeLeave")
<br>
> (link-goto: "I understand. Whatever may come, good luck.", "AlexandraD5Understand")


